<td align="center"><b>
<i>Lasioglossum sopinci</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Crawford, 1932&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Halictus sopinci </i>Crawford, 1932; <i>Evylaeus sopinci </i>&#40;Crawford, 1932&#41;</small><p>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Hymenoptera">Hymenoptera</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Apoidea">Apoidea</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Halictidae">Halictidae</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Lasioglossum">Lasioglossum</a>
<br><small>Subgenus: <a href="/mp/20p?see=Hemihalictus&name=Lasioglossum&flags=subgenus:"><i>Hemihalictus</i></a></small>
